This is a map based of the game portal. It has some new things for gg. I think its balanced mostly. 
Notes about this map:
-bridge can be broken
-acid pits do kill you
-spawn killing won't happen
-camping at spawn won't work either
-portals take you both ways.
-can't shoot people though portals :P

 Pm if there are bugs with the portals. The cake is a lie :D
have fun
